_refine.details                                  
;The purpose of the present study was to unumbiguously identify a metal ion as zinc. 
Therefore a data set including the anomlaous data was collected at the zinc absorption edge. 
The structure is virtually identical to the entry 1PVY. Therefore, a simple refinement was
sufficient to "solve" the structure. The strcuture was refined against the
data set, not containing the anomalous data.
